body_content.explanation: the quality of seeming very strange and not at all familiar:
examples: A sense of mystery pervades the film, particularly the looming alienness of the mountain.
I had no idea what "albedo" meant and was struck by the sheer alienness of the word.

body_content.explanation: the quality of belonging to or coming from a place, country, group of people, or planet that is not your own and is not familiar:
examples: Unlike many European colonials, he was not at all disturbed by the alienness of Africa.
